---
title: Kung Pao Mushrooms with Jasmine Rice and Chili Cashews
description: Traditionally made with chicken, Kung Pao is a spicy stir-fry dish that is found throughout China. We've switched it up into a vegetarian version using meaty mushrooms and broccoli, and topped it all off with some chili cashews - delicious!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/kung-pao-mushrooms-f2a1f5d9.jpg
